		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">H.O.P.E.</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>HOPE</b> (abbreviation <b>Hackers on Planet Earth</b> or the first two letters in Hotel Pennsylvania) is a <a href="/wiki/Meeting" title="Meeting">conference</a> series sponsored by the <a href="/wiki/Hacker_(computer_security)" title="Hacker (computer security)">hacker</a> magazine <i><a href="/wiki/2600_The_Hacker_Quarterly" title="2600 The Hacker Quarterly" class="mw-redirect">2600 The Hacker Quarterly</a>.</i> There have been seven conferences to date.</p>
